# Cleric Domain Spell List

**Editorial note:** This document has been cleaned of advertisements and reformatted for use as a source reference. The following typographical corrections have been made from the original: *Creats* → *Creates* (Darkness domain); *may be lowed* → *may be slowed* (Earth domain); *Slight of Hand* → *Sleight of Hand* (Greed domain); *Dessication/dessication* → *Desiccation/desiccation* (Summer/Purification domains).

