| --- | --- | --- |
| 1 | Lesser Confusion: One creature confused for 1 round | Protection from Law: +2 AC/saves, counter mind control. |
| 2 | Entropic Shield: Ranged attacks against you have 20% miss chance | Resist Planar Alignment: Resist penalties for opposing alignment on aligned plane. |
| 3 | Magic Circle against Law: 10-ft. radius, 10 min./level | Mantle of Chaos: SR 12 + caster level against lawful-descriptor spells. |
| 4 | Chaos Hammer: Damage and slow lawful creatures | Perinarch: Gain greater control over Limbo’s morphic essence. |
| 5 | Baleful Polymorph: Transforms subject into harmless animal | Dispel Law: +4 bonus against attacks by lawful creatures. |
| 6 | Animate Objects: Objects attack your foes | Insanity: Subject suffers continuous confusion effect. |
| 7 | Song of Discord: Forces targets to attack each other | Word of Chaos: Kills, confuses, stuns, or deafens nonchaotic subjects. |
| 8 | Cloak of Chaos: +4 AC/resistance, SR 25 against lawful spells | Otto’s Irresistible Dance: Forces subject to dance. |
| 9 | Perinarch, Planar: Gain control over small area of any divinely morphic plane | Shapechange: Transforms you into any creature; change forms once per round. |

